OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine
OL,7,Fbut cloud along eastern Aberdeenshire
OL,8,Fcoast gradually edging inland tonight
OL,9,Fwith some mist, but well inland
OL,10,Fstaying clear.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FLow cloud in north and east
OL,13,Fburning back to coast once again where
OL,14,Fpatches may linger, otherwise long
OL,15,Fspells of unbroken sunshine. Warm
OL,16,Finland, coastal districts cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
