OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudier
OL,6,Fon Friday but south and west becoming
OL,7,Fsunnier in afternoon. Cloudy start on
OL,8,FSaturday, chance of a light shower,
OL,9,Fthen sunny. Sunday starting sunny then
OL,10,Fclouding over. Cooler
